Package: agnetic-os
Version: 0.1.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-pip, python3-venv, curl
Recommends: ollama, nats-server
Suggests: nvidia-cuda-toolkit | rocm-dev
Maintainer: Agnetic Starship OS <starship@agnetic.os>
Homepage: https://github.com/andromi-hash/agnetic-os
Description: Agnetic Starship OS
 An AI agent-first operating system. Local AI agents communicate via
 NATS/JetStream message bus with GPU-accelerated inference through Ollama.
 Includes: agneticctl CLI, StarAgent telemetry collector, 3 agent daemons
 (proxy, romi, ergo), web dashboard, and GPU detection.
 Built for Ubuntu 24.04 LTS. Supports NVIDIA and AMD GPUs.
